nodes.text: As part of the Imperial–Grysk conflict, a battle between forces of the Grysk Hegemony and the allied forces of the Galactic Empire and Chiss Ascendancy occurred deep within Imperial space. The Grysk forces were scouting the strengths and weaknesses of the Imperial Navy to report back to the Grysk homeworld, but were destroyed thanks to the timely dispatch of TIE Defenders.
